cdi = read.csv("data/cdi.csv")


cdi_cor = cdi %>% 
  select(-id,-cty,-state)
cdi.cor = cor(cdi_cor)


library(corrplot)
## corrplot 0.92 loaded
corrplot(cdi.cor)
